title: Match History Not Updating
body:
Hello,

For the past 3 games or so my match history hasn't been updating. Reset the client, it's been a while, they still aren't showing up. Is anyone else having this problem or is it just me?  

Thank you!

Dmkeaz

replies.body:
Hey there,

I believe NA was temporarily experiencing an issue that was causing this.

Have the matches appeared now?
